OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1780992973
OL,3,CCharity caring for 50+ guinea pigs
OL,4,Cafter population explosion in woman's
OL,5,Cshed
OL,7,FWatch: More than 50 guinea pigs are
OL,8,Fnow in the care of the Blue Cross in
OL,9,FOxfordshire, as ITV News Meridian's
OL,10,FNatalie Verney reports
OL,12,FAn animal charity in Oxfordshire has
OL,13,Fdoubled the number of guinea pigs in
OL,14,Fits care, after more than 200 were
OL,15,Ftaken from a woman's home.
OL,17,FThe woman, from Wales, raised the
OL,18,Falarm with her local animal charity
OL,19,Fafter she found she was dealing with
OL,20,Fan accidental population explosion.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
