PN,41502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1780992973
OL,3,CCharity caring for 50+ guinea pigs
OL,4,Cafter population explosion in woman's
OL,5,Cshed
OL,7,FThe Blue Cross in Burford is one of 22
OL,8,Fcharities that came to the rescue of
OL,9,Fthe 224 guinea pigs who were living in
OL,10,Fher shed.
OL,12,FThe Oxfordshire charity has taken on
OL,13,F56 of them, but that number could
OL,14,Falmost double in a few weeks, because
OL,15,Fmany are pregnant.
OL,17,FAnouska Ashmead-Bartlett from the Blue
OL,18,FCross Rehoming Centre said: "It can be
OL,19,Fquite difficult quite quickly to get
OL,20,Fout of control - especially when they
OL,21,Fcan breed so quickly.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1780992973
OL,3,CCharity caring for 50+ guinea pigs
OL,4,Cafter population explosion in woman's
OL,5,Cshed
OL,7,F"It is important to ensure that pets
OL,8,Fare neutered when they need to be and
OL,9,Fare split into same-sex groups."
OL,11,FStaff say caring for them all is a
OL,12,Fnever-ending cycle of feeding and
OL,13,Fcleaning, with twice as many meaning
OL,14,Ftwice as much food.
OL,16,FThe logistics of finding space for
OL,17,Fthem all has also been a challenge.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
