FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1780992973
OL,3,CCharity caring for 50+ guinea pigs
OL,4,Cafter population explosion in woman's
OL,5,Cshed
OL,7,FAnouska said: "We have had to move
OL,8,Fsome animals around to create space
OL,9,Ffor the guinea pigs and change some
OL,10,Faccommodation to fit them.
OL,12,F"All of the team have got involved
OL,13,Ffrom other sections, management have
OL,14,Fgot involved, and people have come in
OL,15,Fearly to support in cleaning and
OL,16,Ffeeding them, so it is a real team
OL,17,Feffort to support all the guinea pigs."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
