PN,41505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1780992973
OL,3,CCharity caring for 50+ guinea pigs
OL,4,Cafter population explosion in woman's
OL,5,Cshed
OL,7,FThey have now been split into more
OL,8,Fthan 20 different enclosures, with
OL,9,Fmales and females kept separate to
OL,10,Fensure there is no more multiplying.
OL,12,FHowever, as some of the guinea pigs
OL,13,Fare already pregnant, staff are
OL,14,Fbracing themselves for the arrival of
OL,15,Fdozens of new pups in the coming weeks.
OL,17,FThe team is confident they will be
OL,18,Fable to find them all new homes.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
