OL,3,CCharity caring for 50+ guinea pigs
OL,4,Cafter population explosion in woman's
OL,5,Cshed
OL,7,FAnouska said: "I think they're
OL,8,Ffabulous. The noises they make are
OL,9,Fgreat. They're really really lovely
OL,10,Fanimals to have around which has made
OL,11,Four jobs a lot easier as well."
